{"tid":1291112,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"推到傳媒去採訪美國著名學者及政治哲學家Noam Chomsky","createTime":"2019-07-06T17:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T17:54:38.000Z","uid":266916,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc472523746edb89c567f721f03c7c26740023e","tid":1291112,"uid":266916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"美國著名學者及政治哲學家諾姆．喬姆斯基（Noam Chomsky）鼓勵港人的訊息。喬姆斯基指：「我一直密切關注（香港的消息）。年輕人在反修例抗爭行動中展現出莫大的勇氣及氣節。雖然有幸獲得國際支持，可是抗爭者對於中國的逼迫依然無計可施。」雖然他並未就香港和蘇丹民眾抗爭等大事撰文，但有機會的話他樂意在接受訪談時提出相關意見。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyv39u7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftyv39u7.jpg&h=403982ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreedomhkgofficial%2Fposts%2F345252002816624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Ffreedomhkgofficial%252Fposts%252F345252002816624&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzRxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=2c601200\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreedomhkgofficial%2Fposts%2F345252002816624</a><br />\n佢真係一個好權威既學者，而家唔輕易接受訪問，但係而家佢主動話有興趣。<br />\n如果做到佢既訪問，將會係一鼓好強既外國勢力！<br />\n快啲推到媒體出手做嘢！"},{"pid":"4bea9c5b29d9b5731034f3bbe3fac28828ce51e0","tid":1291112,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"<code>我冇野講</code>"},{"pid":"7be9df00a3529c161d33ccf4b61deb8bb1b50237","tid":1291112,"uid":266916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"btw, 原來轉名都會變P牌？"},{"pid":"59477306d5043ae779a707b12b2a79786e6f56ba","tid":1291112,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:45:20.000Z","msg":"skype 採訪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c12d9521798102c54224d6fd89f948dbbb193a","tid":1291112,"uid":125027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<br />\n但教授佢有野講"},{"pid":"29626550ff5ab023a208a401f485cc20ca5d1fdc","tid":1291112,"uid":60166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:54:25.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，連Chomsky都有關注香港咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936a7b6168c1630cf8014cb8df46ef4a8e23b35b","tid":1291112,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:54:38.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔知佢有冇咩抗中妙計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}